{"tid":1809130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「黃色經濟圈」注定是一個笑話","createTime":"2020-01-03T01:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T05:18:42.000Z","uid":83164,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2976edaa7c3fc87a971671e2e72f9dca5a71cf48","tid":1809130,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:07:19.000Z","msg":"人民日報發表文章，認為所謂「黃色經濟圈」注定是一個笑話。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，黃色經濟圈剝奪市民消費選擇的自由，亦損傷市民經營活動的自由，在商界刮起黑色恐怖之風，黃色經濟圈只是幌子，只是排除異己的手段，批評反中亂港分子想要的只是「攬炒」，是香港經濟的衰敗、社會文明的崩塌、法治精神的潰敗。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，當衣食住行都要被迫「選邊站」，暴徒的面目、暴力的危害已經一清二楚，越來越多市民認識到黃色經濟圈的荒謬與腐朽，陸續「割席」，重申止暴制亂是刻不容緩，市民應該擦亮眼睛，讓香港重現文明之光、法治之光，恢復現代化國際大都市應有的樣子，包容多元，自由開放。"},{"pid":"ed6bf5efd1cc7089d54e1e9f27805a4bf463e67f","tid":1809130,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>借個位用</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>●○●○由窮爸爸富爸爸探討黃色經濟圈發展●○●○</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1801758/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1801758/</a><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>●○●○由澶淵之盟探討黃色經濟圈發展●○●○</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1808346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1808346</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>●○●○黃色證券圈●○●○</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1798024\" data-auto-link target=\"